0with%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20geopolitical%20partner%26quot%3B%20like%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20called%20it%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bunwise%20decisions%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20case%20rests%20on%20the%20allegation%20that%20preparations%20were%20made%20by%20members%20of%20this%20company%20in%20India%20to%20bribe%20Indian%20officials%2C%20also%20exclusively%20located%20in%20India.%20Instead%20of%20deferring%20the%20case%20to%20the%20appropriate%20Indian%20authorities%2C%20the%20Biden%20DoJ%20decided%20to%20push%20forward%20and%20indict%20the%20company's%20executives%20without%20any%20real%20injury%20to%20US%20interests%20being%20present%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congressmen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20compelling%20reason%26quot%3B%20to%20pursue%20a%20case%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20could%20complicate%20relations%20with%20an%20ally%20like%20India%20unless%20some%20external%20factors%20were%20at%20play%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20misguided%20crusade%20came%20at%20the%20risk%20of%20harming%20our%20relationship%20with%20a%20strategic%20geopolitical%20partner%20like%20India%20immediately%20preceding%20President%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20Oval%20Office%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20that%20considering%20Donald%20Trump's%20commitment%20to%20revive%20America's%20economic%20prosperity%2C%20their%20economic%20relationship%20with%20%26quot%3Bvaluable%20partners%26quot%3B%20from%20India%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20factor%26quot%3B%20in%20achieving%20that%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeedless%20pursuits%20against%20those%20who%20have%20contributed%20tens%20of%20billions%20and%20created%20thousands%20of%20jobs%20deter%20and%20discourage%20investors%20from%20contributing%20to%20our%20economy.%20Considering%20these%20factors%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20any%20real%20injury%20to%20U.S.%20interests%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20pursue%20this%20indictment%20demonstrates%20more%20harm%20for%20America's%20interests%20than%20good%2C%20if%20any%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congressmen%20said%20that%20the%20US%20and%20India%20share%20a%20sense%20of%20mutual%20respect%20and%20appreciation%20-%20a%20sentiment%20emulated%20by%20President%20Trump%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20has%20always%20recognized%20the%20true%20potential%20of%20a%20strong%20and%20beneficial%20relationship%20between%20two%20economic%20and%20military%20superpowers%20like%20the%20US%20and%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote%20in%20a%20two-page%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConversely%2C%20politically%20motivated%20decisions%20by%20agencies%20steered%20by%20left-wing%20megadonors%20could%20quickly%20erode%20years%20of%20hard%20work%20and%20diplomacy%20forged%20by%20our%20leaders.%20A%20fallout%20in%20relations%20not%20only%20harms%20our%20longstanding%20partnership%20with%20a%20key%20ally%20but%20greatly%20benefits%20adversaries%20like%20China%20in%20their%20goal%20to%20eliminate%20the%20American%20economy%20and%20achieve%20total%20global%20economic%20control%20through%20their%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%26quot%3Bselective%20pursuit%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Biden%20DoJ%2C%20despite%20knowing%20the%20possible%20outcomes%20of%20such%20a%20%26quot%3Breckless%20decision%26quot%3B%2C%20requires%20a%20second%20look%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20request%20you%20investigate%20the%20Biden%20DOJ's%20conduct%20and%20would%20appreciate%20you%20sharing%20with%20us%20all%20records%20pertaining%20to%20this%20case%2C%20for%20a%20coordinated%20effort%20in%20uncovering%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%2