0Ahmedabad%20in%20February%202020.%20PM%20Modi%20was%20also%20among%20the%20top%20three%20world%20leaders%20to%20speak%20with%20Mr%20Trump%20after%20his%20stunning%20electoral%20victory%20in%20November%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20his%20departure%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20recalled%20his%20previous%20collaboration%20with%20Mr%20Trump%20during%20the%20Republican%20leader's%20first%20presidential%20term%20and%20expressed%20eagerness%20to%20meet%20him%20again.%20%26quot%3BAlthough%20this%20will%20be%20our%20first%20meeting%20following%20his%20historic%20electoral%20victory%20and%20inauguration%20in%20January%2C%20I%20have%20a%20very%20warm%20recollection%20of%20working%20together%20in%20his%20first%20term%20in%20building%20a%20Comprehensive%20Global%20Strategic%20Partnership%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasised%20that%20the%20visit%20would%20provide%20an%20opportunity%20to%20build%20on%20past%20successes%20and%20develop%20a%20forward-looking%20agenda%20in%20key%20sectors%20such%20as%20trade%2C%20defence%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20supply%20chain%20resilience.%20%26quot%3BThis%20visit%20will%20be%20an%20opportunity%20to%20build%20upon%20the%20successes%20of%20our%20collaboration%20in%20his%20first%20term%20and%20develop%20an%20agenda%20to%20further%20elevate%20and%20deepen%20our%20partnership%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20PM%20Modi's%20Washington%20tour%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20are%20expected%20to%20discuss%20a%20range%20of%20strategic%20issues%2C%20including%20trade%20policies%2C%20defence%20cooperation%2C%20and%20global%20security%20challenges.%20The%20visit%20gains%20significance%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20recent%20policy%20shifts%20in%20the%20US%2C%20including%20deportation%20measures%20affecting%20Indian%20nationals%20and%20discussions%20on%20reciprocal%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20held%20a%20phone%20call%2