0doom%20looms%20over%20the%20future%20of%20Gaza%20and%20Palestinians%20living%20in%20the%20enclave%20as%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20threat%20to%20take%20over%20the%20territory%20and%20end%20the%20fragile%20ceasefire%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20The%20American%20President%20has%20warned%20Hamas%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20hell%20will%20break%20loose%26quot%3B%20following%20its%20threats%20to%20postpone%20the%20exchange%20of%20hostages%20under%20the%20war%20truce%20with%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20stressed%20that%20his%20plan%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20over%20Gaza%26quot%3B%20would%20not%20include%20a%20right%20of%20return%20for%20the%20more%20than%202%20million%20Palestinians%20that%20he%20has%20said%20have%20%26quot%3Bno%20alternative%26quot%3B%20but%20to%20leave%20because%20of%20the%20destruction%20left%20by%20Israel's%20military%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Ceasefire%20Warning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Republican%20leader%20set%20a%20Saturday%20deadline%20for%20all%20hostages%20to%20be%20released%20from%20Gaza%2C%20saying%20that%20otherwise%20%26quot%3Ball%20hell%26quot%3B%20would%20break%20out%20and%20he%20would%20call%20for%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20ceasefire%20to%20be%20cancelled.%20The%20United%20States'%20latest%20extraordinary%20intervention%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20came%20after%20Hamas%20threatened%20to%20postpone%20any%20further%20hostage-prisoner%20exchanges%2C%20placing%20the%20fragile%20six-week%20truce%20that%20took%20effect%20on%20January%2019%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20Hamas's%20move%20as%20%26quot%3Bterrible%26quot%3B%2C%20President%20Trump%20said%20would%20%26quot%3Blet%20that%20be%20Israel's%20decision%26quot%3B%20on%20what%20should%20ultimately%20happen%20to%20the%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20as%20far%20as%20I'm%20concerned%2C%20if%20all%20of%20the%20hostages%20aren't%20returned%20by%20Saturday%2012%20o'