ructured%20traffic%20and%20crowd%20management%20plan.%20He%20also%20directed%20the%20officials%20to%20fully%20utilise%20the%20available%20parking%20capacity%20of%20over%205%20lakh%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLong%20queues%20of%20vehicles%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20form%20on%20roads.%20Traffic%20congestion%20must%20be%20prevented%20at%20all%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20traffic%20advisory%20comes%20following%20a%20stampede%20on%20the%20second%20shahi%20snan%20(holy%20bath)%20on%20Mauni%20Amavasya%20on%20January%2029.%20According%20to%20the%20official%20data%2C%20at%20least%2030%20people%20were%20killed%20and%2060%20injured%20in%20the%20stampede.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20taken%20just%20before%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20stampede%20incident%20shows%20that%20barricades%20were%20set%20up%20along%20the%20road%20to%20prevent%20people%20from%20walking%20directly%20on%20the%20road.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20move%20forward%2C%20the%20crowd%20broke%20the%20barricades%20and%20started%20running%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-member%20judicial%20commission%20has%20been%20appointed%20to%20investigate%20the%20causes%20of%20the%20stampede%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20in%20a%20month.%20The%20panel%20comprises%20Justice%20Harsh%20Kumar%2C%20former%20Director%20General%20VK%20Gupta%2C%20and%20retired%20IAS%20officer%20VK%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20judicial%20probe%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20announced%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20for%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaha%20Kumbh%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20congregation%20of%20people%2C%20began%20on%20January%2013%20and%20will%20continue%20until%20February%2026.%20As%20of%20February%2010%2C%2044.74%20crore%20people%20had%20attended%20the%20Kumbh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739243340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fufjan92_maha-kumbh_625x300_11_Febru