%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Targets%20Indian%20Restaurants%20In%20Trump-Style%20Immigration%20Crackdown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReminiscent%20of%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20tough%20immigration%20crackdown%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdon's%20Labour%20government%20has%20launched%20a%20mass%20raids%20on%20illegal%20working%20in%20the%20country.%20Described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BUK-wide%20blitz%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20crackdown%20has%20extended%20to%20Indian%20restaurants%2C%20nail%20bars%2C%20convenience%20stores%20and%20car%20washes%20which%20employ%20migrant%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20British%20Home%20Secretary%20Yvette%20Cooper%20personally%20overseeing%2C%20the%20Home%20Office%20reported%20a%20record-breaking%20January%2C%20as%20they%20descended%20on%20828%20premises%20--%20a%2048%20per%20cent%20rise%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20January%2C%20with%20arrests%20surging%20to%20609%2C%20and%20marking%20a%2073%20per%20cent%20increase%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Cooper's%20Office%20said%20that%20while%20its%20teams%20respond%20to%20illegal%20working%20intelligence%20in%20all%20sectors%2C%20a%20significant%20proportion%20of%20last%20month's%20activity%20took%20place%20at%20restaurants%2C%20takeaways%20and%20cafes%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20food%2C%20drink%20and%20tobacco%20industry.%20A%20visit%20to%20one%20Indian%20restaurant%20in%20Humberside%2C%20northern%20England%2C%20alone%20led%20to%20seven%20arrests%20and%20four%20detentions%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20immigration%20rules%20must%20be%20respected%20and%20enforced.%20For%20far%20too%20long%2C%20employers%20have%20been%20able%20to%20take%20on%20and%20exploit%20illegal%20migrants%20and%20too%20many%20people%20have%20been%20able%20to%20arrive%20and%20work%20illegally%20with%20no%20enforcement%20action%20ever%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Cooper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20does%20this%20create%20a%20dangerous%20draw%20for%20people%20to%20risk%20their%20lives%20by%20crossing%20the%20Channel%20in%20a%20small%20boat%2C%20but%20it%20results%20in%20the%20abuse%20of%20vulnerable%20people%2C%20the%20immigration%20system%2C%20and%20our%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BShow%2C%20Not%20Tell%20Strategy%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20rapid%20surge%20of%20Reform%20UK%20in%20the%20polls%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20is%20under%20pressure%20to%20prove%20his%20government%20is%20tough%20on%20illegal%20immigration.%20It%20is%20using%20bespoke%20charter%20flights%20to%20remove%20%26quot%3Bimmigration%20offenders%26quot%3B%20to%20countries%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20four%20of%20the%20biggest%20migrant%20returns%20flights%20in%20the%20UK's%20history%20carrying%20more%20than%20800%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20show-not-tell%20strategy%2C%20the%20Starmer%20government%20is%20resorting%20to%20Trump-style%20TV%20footage%20of%20these%20deportation%20flight%20processes%2C%20showing%20men%20to%20be%20deported%20being%20taken%20off%20a%20bus%20and%20up%20the%20stairway%20of%20a%20charter%20jet.%20Those%20removed%20on%20these%20flights%20are%20said%20to%20include%20criminals%20convicted%20of%20drug%20offences%2C%20theft%2C%20rape%20and%20murder.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20released%20a%20video%20showing%20the%20deportation%20of%20migrants%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20as%20it%20marks%20the%20removal%20of%20nearly%2019%2C000%20foreign%20criminals%20and%20illegal%20migrants%20since%20Labour%20took%20office.%20In%20the%20footage%2C%20a%20man's%20hands%20were%20shackled%20as%20he%20was%20escorted%20by%20numerous%20Border%20Force%20staff%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20public%20must%20have%20confidence%20in%20the%20UK's%20immigration%20system.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThrough%20our%20Plan%20for%20Change%2C%20we%20have%20removed%20almost%2019%2C000%20people%20including%20failed%20asylum%20seekers%2C%20foreign%20criminals%20and%20immigration%20offenders%20from%20the%20UK%20since%20July%202024.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQY4tpQDqSP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FQY4tpQDqSP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Home%20Office%20(%40ukhomeoffice)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fukhomeoffice%2Fstatus%2F1888998675415761399%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2010%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20also%20working%20upstream%20to%20deter%20people%20from%20entering%20the%20UK%20illegally%20by%20launching%20a%20new%20international%20campaign%20to%20debunk%20people%20smugglers'%20lies.%20Social%20media%20adverts%20went%20live%20in%20Vietnam%20in%20December%20and%20Albania%20in%20January%2C%20highlighting%20real%20stories%20from%20migrants%20who%20entered%20the%20UK%20illegally%2C%20only%20to%20face%20debt%2C%20exploitation%2C%20and%20a%20life%20far%20from%20what%20they%20were%20promised%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Home%20Office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EImmigration%20Crackdown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20Office%20statistics%20claim%20that%20between%20July%205%20last%20year%20and%20January%2031%20this%20year%2C%20illegal%20working%20crackdowns%20and%20arrests%20have%20soared%20by%20around%2038%20per%20cent%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%2012%20months%20prior.%20A%20total%20of%201%2C090%20civil%20penalty%20notices%20have%20been%20issued%20during%20that%20phase%2C%20with%20employers%20facing%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20GBP%2060%2C000%20per%20worker%20if%20found%20liable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20figures%20demonstrate%20the%20commitment%20of%20my%20teams%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20those%20who%20think%20they%20can%20flout%20our%20immigration%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Eddy%20Montgomery%2C%20Director%20of%20Enforcement%2C%20Compliance%20and%20Crime%20at%20the%20Home%20Office.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20it%20sends%20a%20strong%20signal%20that%20there%20is%20no%20hiding%20place%20from%20the%20law%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20ramp%20up%20our%20activity%20to%20ensure%20those%20involved%20face%20the%20full%20consequences.%E2%80%AF%C2%A0We%20also%20know%20that%20many%20people%20who%20end%20up%20working%20illegally%20are%20often%20subjected%20to%20extremely%20poor%20conditions%2C%20so%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20all%20we%20can%20to%20safeguard%20and%20protect%20the%20most%20vulnerable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20this%20activity%2C%20Immigrant%20Enforcement%20said%20it%20also%20plays%20a%20critical%20safeguarding%20role%20in%20working%20closely%20with%20organisations%20to%20allow%20employees%20to%20report%20labour%20exploitation.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20it%20claimed%20to%20have%20smashed%20its%20target%20to%20drive%20the%20removal%20of%20foreign%20criminals%20and%20immigration%20offenders%20to%20the%20highest%20level%20since%202018%2C%20with%2016%2C400%20people%20removed%20since%20the%20July%202024%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUK's%20Border%20Security%2C%20Asylum%20and%20Immigration%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20raids%20come%20as%20the%20Labour%20Party%20government's%20Border%20Security%2C%20Asylum%20and%20Immigration%20Bill%20returns%20to%20Parliament%20for%20its%20second%20reading%20this%20week.%20The%20new%20legislation%20aims%20to%20%26quot%3Bsmash%20the%20criminal%20gangs%26quot%3B%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer-led%20administration%20says%20undermines%20border%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Border%20Security%2C%20Asylum%20and%20Immigration%20Bill%20is%20designed%20to%20grant%20law%20enforcement%20additional%20powers%20to%20take%20earlier%20and%20more%20effective%20action%20against%20organ