ly%20to%20be%20decided%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20which%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20deadline%20for%20submission%20of%20the%20final%20squads%20to%20the%20ICC.%20Bumrah%2C%20India's%20best%20performer%20in%20the%202024-25%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%2C%20has%20been%20sidelined%20due%20to%20injury%20since%20the%20final%20Test%20of%20the%20series.%20The%20star%20fast%20bowler%20had%20to%20pull%20out%20mid-match%20after%20he%20felt%20pain%20in%20his%20back%20while%20bowling%20in%20Sydney%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20January.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20not%20played%20any%20cricket%20match.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20was%20named%20in%20the%20India%20squad%20for%20the%20third%20ODI%20against%20England%20(on%20Wednesday%20in%20Ahmedabad)and%20also%20in%20the%20provisional%20squad%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Findia-likely-to-take-decision-on-jasprit-bumrah-for-champions-trophy-on-tuesday-1472739%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EESPNCricinfo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bumrah%20recently%20underwent%20a%20scan%20of%20his%20back%20at%20the%20BCCI's%20Centre%20of%20Excellence%20in%20Bengaluru.%20The%20report%20also%20claimed%20that%20BCCI%20medical%20staff%20will%20now%20give%20the%20details%20to%20the%20selectors%20and%20the%20team%20management.%20A%20final%20decision%20may%20be%20taken%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20claimed%20that%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Harshit%20Rana%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F115601-harshit-rana-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHarshit%20Rana%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20named%20Bumrah's%20replacement%20if%20the%20latter%20does%20not%20get%20fit%20on%20time.%20Tuesday%20is%20the%20last%20date%20the%20teams%20can%20change%20their%20squads%20without%20any%20approval%20from%20the%20tournament's%20technical%20committee.%20After%20that%2C%20if%20a%20change%20needs%20to%20be%20made%2C%20the%20ICC%20will%20have%20to%20be%20informed%20and%20permission%20needs%20to%20be%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20team%20would%20wait%20till%20the%20last%20moment%20in%20order%20to%20get%20him%20ready%20for%20the%20marquee%20ICC%20event.%20%26quot%3BStrength%20and%20Conditioning%20(S%26amp%3BC)%20coach%20Rajnikanth%20Sivagnanam%20and%20physio%20Thulasi%20Ram%20Yuvraj%20are%20currently%20working%20on%20Bumrah's%20rehabilitation%20with%20Head%20of%20Sports%20Science%2C%20Dr%20Nitin%20Patel%2C%20personally%20monitoring%20the%20whole%20process.%20Obviously%2C%20the%20national%20team%20S%26amp%3BC%20coach%20Soham%20Desai%20and%20physio%20Kamlesh%20Jain%20are%20also%20kept%20in%20the%20loop%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20BCCI%20official%20told%20the%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Bumrah%20does%20not%20play%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20a%20massive%20blow%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%2C%20who%20are%20desperate%20for%20a%20morale-boosting%20win%20after%20repeated%20losses%20since%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20win%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBumrah%20not%20fit%20will%20reduce%20India's%20chances%20(of%20winning%20the%20Champions%20Trophy)%20by%2030%20percent%2C%20literally%20by%2030-35%20percent.%20With%20a%20fully%20fit%20Bumrah%20playing%2C%20you%20are%20guaranteed%20of%20those%20deathovers.%20It%20would've%20been%20a%20different%20ball%20game%20altogether%2C%26quot%3B%20opined%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Shastri%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41719-ravishankar-jayadritha-shastri-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavi%20Shastri%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20India%20coach%2C%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739238900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fso18koi8_bumrah-bcci_625x300_12_January_25.jpg%22%2C%2