titive%20ski%20career%20but%20kicked%20off%20my%20interest%20in%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I'm%20a%20double-board-certified%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-shares-how-she-maintains-muscle-stays-active-with-age-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoctor%20in%20sports%20medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20physical%20medicine%20and%20rehabilitation.%20I'm%20one%20of%20the%20doctors%20who%20treat%20the%20US%20Ski%20Team.%20In%20my%20work%2C%20I'm%20seeing%20more%20discussion%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20hormones%20on%20sports%20injuries%20for%20women.%20Here's%20what%20we%20know%20about%20the%20role%20of%20hormones%20in%20injury%20and%20how%20to%20prevent%20getting%20hurt%20on%20the%20slopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221e76b165-56c9-400e-9e3d-9af305c2eb2e%5C%22%3EWomen%20are%20more%20prone%20to%20ACL%20injury%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20are%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC4805849%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20twice%20as%20likely%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-recovered-torn-acl-skiing-accident-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etear%20their%20ACLs%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20men%20are%20%E2%80%94%20in%20fact%2C%20some%20research%20puts%20the%20risk%20much%20higher%2C%20at%20eight%20times%20the%20risk%20men%20have.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20reasons%20for%20this.%20Women%20tend%20to%20have%20wider%20hips%20than%20men%2C%20which%20impacts%20the%20knee%20angle.%20Anatomically%2C%20this%20can%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20ACL%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20broadly%20speaking%2C%20women%20have%20less%20neuromuscular%20control%20than%20men.%20Boys%20are%20often%20encouraged%20into%20sports%20like%20weightlifting%20and%20biologically%20have%20more%20muscle%20mass.%20Women%20tend%20toward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessional-figure-skater-on-how-pain-altered-her-life-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esports%20like%20figure%20skating%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20dancing%2C%20where%20strength%20isn't%20the%20priority.%20Since%20muscle%20strength%20provides%20stability%2C%20many%20women%20have%20less%20stability%20in%20their%20ACLs%20compared%20to%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22607ec158-1427-469b-bfb2-b85a629248a7%5C%22%3EHormones%20play%20a%20role%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHormones%20are%20also%20at%20play.%20We%20need%20more%20research%20on%20this%2C%20but%20a%20few%20studies%20suggest%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-periods-menstrual-cycle-affect-fat-loss-muscle-building-fitness-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20injure%20their%20ACLs%20when%20they're%20ovulating%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20time%20of%20the%20menstrual%20cycle%20when%20estrogen%20is%20highest.%20Estrogen%20can%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC6341375%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20make%20ligaments%20less%20stiff%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20increasing%20the%20risk%20for%20injury.%20This%20is%20the%20same%20reason%20women%20might%20experience%20ligament%20injuries%20during%20pregnancy.%20Since%20body%20temperature%20also%20increases%20during%20ovulation%2C%20the%20body%20may%20be%20more%20prone%20to%20inflammation%20and%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20we%20would%20never%20blame%20an%20ACL%20injury%20purely%20on%20hormones.%20But%2C%20increased%20estrogen%20combined%20with%20fatigue%2C%20lack%20of%20muscle%20control%2C%20and%20biomechanical%20strains%20on%20the%20ligament%20can%20have%20an%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20women%20aren't%20the%20only%20ones%20with%20a%20correlation%20between%20hormone%20changes%20and%20injury.%20For%20males%2C%20increased%20testosterone%20can%20increase%20competitiveness%20or%20risk-taking%20behavior%2C%20creating%20more%20risk%20for%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22415d8304-eaf9-42f4-888e-6f38055ff3bd%5C%22%3EDynamic%20exercises%20can%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFlexibility%20is%20often%20celebrated%2C%20but%20without%20stability%2C%20it's%20not%20great.%20Women%20%E2%80%94%20and%20everyone%20else%20%E2%80%94%20need%20flexibility%20and%20stability%20to%20protect%20their%20ligaments.%20Building%20strength%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20increase%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFocus%20on%20exercises%20that%20mimic%20the%20real%20world%20and%20use%20multiple%20muscle%20groups%20simultaneously.%20Squats%20and%20leg%20presses%20are%20great%20examples.%20These%20exercises%20train%20multiple%20muscle%20groups%20to%20work%20together%20and%20respond%20to%20different%20stimuli.%20That%20will%20help%20on%20the%20slopes%20when%20you%20need%20to%20suddenly%20navigate%20around%20other%20skiers%2C%20stay%20steady%20on%20a%20patch%20of%20ice%2C%20or%20land%20a%20jump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227988ea3c-5308-41ae-8d70-e508e42ff95d%5C%22%3EQuit%20while%20you're%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20notice%20you're%20tired%20during%20an%20exercise%2C%20your%20muscles%20are%20already%20fatigued.%20That%20reduces%20your%20performance%2C%20and%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20so%20many%20injuries%20happen%20on%20the%20last%20run%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%2C%20no%20bear%20is%20chasing%20you.%20You%20can%20always%20ski%20another%20day%2C%20so%20don't%20push%20it%20once%20you%20begin%20to%20feel%20tired.%20Head%20to%20the%20lodge%20and%20enjoy%20apr%C3%A8s%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a534e03f-2744-4522-898b-cac618a1b8ee%5C%22%3EBe%20mindful%20of%20whole-body%20changes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you're%20on%20the%20national%20ski%20team%20or%20hitting%20the%20slopes%20as%20a%20casual%20hobby%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20changes%20to%20the%20whole%20body%20during%20your%20menstrual%20cycle%2C%20pregnancy%2C%20and%20menopause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20my%20first%20baby%2015%