uller%20after%20use%20and%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPaper%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20used%20each%20knife%20to%20cut%20through%20a%20sheet%20of%20printer%20paper%20to%20see%20if%20it%20made%20clean%2C%20smooth%20cuts%20or%20tore.%20We%20also%20noted%20whether%20we%20had%20to%20apply%20pressure%20to%20start%20the%20cuts%20or%20if%20the%20knives%20were%20able%20to%20cut%20through%20it%20easily.%20This%20revealed%20how%20sharp%20the%20knives%20were%20out%20of%20the%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESteak%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20cooked%204%20pounds%20of%20skirt%20steak%20(one%20of%20the%20toughest%20cuts)%20and%2012%20links%20of%20Italian%20sausage%20and%20used%20each%20knife%20to%20cut%20through%20both.%20We%20noted%20whether%20they%20made%20clean%20cuts%20through%20the%20meat%2C%20or%20tore%20it%20leaving%20jagged%20edges.%20All%20of%20the%20meat%20was%20cut%20on%20stoneware%20dinner%20plates%2C%20which%20can%20be%20rougher%20on%20knives%20than%20other%20cutting%20surfaces%2C%20like%20a%20cutting%20board.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDuring%20our%20cutting%20tests%2C%20we%20considered%20how%20the%20knives%20felt%20to%20hold%20and%20cut%20with%2C%20if%20they%20were%20comfortable%20in%20the%20hand%2C%20and%20whether%20they%20felt%20secure.%20We%20evaluated%20the%20size%20of%20the%20blade%2C%20handle%2C%20and%20full%20construction%20to%20determine%20how%20that%20effected%20the%20knife's%20performance%20and%20weight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20sharpen%20steak%20knives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAbsolutely.%20How%20you%20sharpen%20them%20depends%20on%20whether%20your%20knives%20are%20serrated%20or%20straight-edged.%20Straight-edged%20knives%20can%20be%20sharpened%20using%20any%20of%20the%20methods%20you%20would%20use%20on%20a%20chef's%20knife%3B%20a%20handheld%20sharpener%2C%20a%20whetstone%2C%20or%20a%20honing%20steel%20(check%20out%20our%20picks%20for%