setups%20even%20as%20some%20big%20names%20mandate%20a%20return%20to%20the%20office.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOliver%20Shaw's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frto-mandate-wfh-breaking-employer-boss-worker-trust-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommute%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20190%20miles%20and%20takes%20more%20than%202%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20absolutely%20fine%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20of%20the%20software%20company%20Orgvue%20travels%20by%20train%20from%20his%20home%20near%20Manchester%2C%20England%2C%20to%20London%2C%20generally%20on%20Tuesdays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShaw%20often%20then%20stays%20overnight%20near%20the%20office%2C%20takes%20a%20return%20train%20after%20work%20the%20next%20day%2C%20and%20gets%20back%20home%20at%20about%2010%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20not%20fine%2C%20however%2C%20in%20Shaw's%20view%2C%20is%20to%20say%20that%20those%20who%20live%20far%20from%20the%20office%20%E2%80%94%20like%20he%20does%20%E2%80%94%20get%20out%20of%20having%20to%20commute%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20at%20many%20employers%2C%20that's%20what%20happens%3A%20Live%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-requiring-return-to-office-rto-mandate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclose%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20show%20up.%20Live%20far%20away%2C%20stay%20remote.%20Where%20the%20boundary%20lies%2C%20however%2C%20is%20often%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-return-to-office-five-days-week-rto-michael-dell-2025-1%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDell%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20Michael%20Dell%20said%20that%20starting%20in%20March%2C%20the%20company%20would%20expect%20workers%20living%20within%20roughly%20an%20hour%20of%20an%20office%20to%20show%20up%20five%20days%20a%20week.%20A%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20guidance%20remains%20in%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeantime%2C%3Cspan%3E%20the%20federal%20government%20is%20giving%20different%20consideration%2C%20at%20least%20initially%2C%20to%20workers%20living%20more%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-federal-return-to-office-mandate-workers-living-far-guidance-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E50%20miles%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20an%20office.%20The%20real%20estate%20company%20Redfin%20has%20drawn%20the%20mark%20at%2020%20miles.%20Last%20year%2C%20IBM%20moved%20to%20require%20managers%20in%20the%20US%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fibm-wants-managers-return-office-or-get-new-job-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20within%2050%20miles%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20an%20office%20or%20a%20client%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be2fbc4d-04e8-470b-bfc4-958069f0e37a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStay%20inside%20the%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Density%2C%20a%20Bay%20Area%20company%20that%20makes%20radar%20sensors%20for%20anonymously%20monitoring%20office%20space%20use%2C%20offered%20relocation%20assistance%20to%20most%20of%20its%20remote%20workers%20so%20they%20could%20regularly%20report%20to%20its%20main%20office%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20and%20large%2C%20if%20you%20didn't%20relocate%2C%20then%20you%20found%20another%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Andrew%20Farah%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20take%20a%20reasonably%20hard%20policy%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20January%2C%20Density%20has%20required%20workers%20who%20live%20within%2030%20miles%20of%20its%20San%20Francisco%20office%20to%20be%20in%20four%20days%20a%20week%20%E2%80%94%20Wednesdays%20are%20a%20work-from-anywhere%20day%20%E2%80%94%20from%2010%20a.m.%20to%203%20p.m.%20That's%20an%20extra%20in-office%20day%20from%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20who%20live