20don't%20draw%20a%20circle%20around%20the%20office%20to%20determine%20who%20has%20to%20come%20in%2C%20Brian%20Elliott%2C%20a%20former%20executive%20at%20Slack%20who%20is%20CEO%20of%20Work%20Forward%2C%20an%20advisory%20firm%20on%20future-of-work%20issues%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20employers%20will%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20you%20all%20to%20be%20together%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20enforce%20it%20through%20monitoring%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20Elliott%20said%2C%20employers%20are%20using%20%26quot%3Bquestionable%20logic%26quot%3B%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbosses-expect-remote-hybrid-workers-in-office-2025-rto-survey-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimplementing%20RTO%20policies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20that%20before%20they%20settle%20on%20a%20line%20of%20demarcation%2C%20employers%20would%20be%20wise%20to%20determine%20which%20teams%20are%20located%20in%20the%20same%20areas%20so%20that%20people%20who%20work%20closely%20together%20might%20meet%20in%20person%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20workers%20would%20understand%20the%20need%20for%20that%2C%20he%20said.%20Yet%2C%20Elliott%20said%2C%20asking%20those%20who%20might%20do%20half%20of%20their%20work%20or%20more%20with%20people%20in%20other%20locations%20to%20show%20up%20often%20strikes%20employees%20as%20illogical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20basically%20commuting%20to%20the%20same%20thing%20you%20would%20have%20been%20doing%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Elliott%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273374332-fac0-46ac-9922-ed0b22e66ca0%5C%22%3EOpening%20an%20office%20but%20going%20hybrid%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProdoscore%2C%20which%20makes%20software%20for%20monitoring%20employee%20productivity%2C%20has%20operated%20as%20a%20remote%20company%20though%20it%20plans%20to%20open%20an%20office%20in%20Boston%20for%20some%20functions%2C%20CEO%20Sam%20Naficy%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20even%2