A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Dissent%20In%20Karnataka%20Unit%2C%20BJP%20Stands%20By%20Party%20Chief%20Vijayendra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20backed%20its%20Karnataka%20leader%20amid%20massive%20infighting%20in%20the%20state%20unit%2C%20reprimanding%20one%20rebel%20and%20issuing%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20to%20another.%20Snubbing%20those%20who%20have%20been%20pushing%20for%20the%20replacement%20of%20BY%20Vijayendra%20as%20the%20party%20chief%2C%20the%20BJP's%20central%20leadership%20has%20refused%20to%20entertain%20their%20complaints%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20party%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20your%20continuing%20tirade%20and%20breach%20of%20discipline%2C%20in%20clear%20contravention%20of%20the%20discipline%20code%20in%20the%20party%20constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20show%20cause%20notice%20to%20Vijayapura%20MLA%20Basanagouda%20Patil%20Yatmal%2C%20to%20which%20he%20has%20to%20reply%20within%2072%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20chief%20has%20been%20facing%20challenge%20from%20hardliners%20since%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20all%20factions%20of%20the%20party%20have%20gone%20to%20Delhi%20to%20meet%20the%20party%20high%20command.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rebel%20camp%2C%20including%20MLAs%20Basanagouda%20Patil%20Yatnal%2C%20BP%20Harish%2C%20former%20MLA%20Kumar%20Bangarappa%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20GM%20Siddeshwara%2C%20%C2%A0had%20also%20planned%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20against%20Karnataka%20state%20in-charge%20Radha%20Mohan%20Das%20Agarwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20the%20central%20leaders%2C%20upset%20with%20the%20row%20in%20the%20only%20southern%20state%20where%20the%20party%20has%20a%20footprint%2C%20refused%20to%20meet%20the%20rebel%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20managed%20to%20meet%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20MP%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20take%20the%20lead.%20But%20reports%20said%20Mr%20Bomma