g%20a%20lakh%20and%20a%20half%20every%20month%20to%20finance%20his%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20treatment%2C%20and%20he%20was%20very%20close%20to%20losing%20hope.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20I%20managed%20to%20run%20my%20home%20for%20those%2012%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20But%20the%20kindness%20of%20the%20world%20kept%20him%20going%2C%20and%20today%2C%20through%20ORDI%2C%20he%20is%20attempting%20to%20be%20that%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20a%20parent%20who%20needs%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20clinch%20the%20argument%20that%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20cure%20for%20rare%20diseases%2C%20Prasanna%20has%20a%20counter-rhetoric%3A%20%E2%80%9CGive%20them%20relief%20then.%E2%80%9D%20Through%20their%20work%2C%20ORDI%20is%20challenging%20the%20notion%20that%20the%20journey%20with%20rare%20diseases%20is%20a%20fight%20to%20be%20won.%20Instead%2C%20they%20emphasise%20making%20the%20battle%20less%20painful.%20One%20of%20their%20most%20significant%20strides%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F162706%2Fbengaluru-pil-supreme-court-rare-disease-father-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eensuring%20access%20to%20court-approved%20medical%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20children%20with%20rare%20diseases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchangemakers-india-1738844473.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Rare%20Diseases%20Care%20Coordination%20Centre%20(RDCCC)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20centres%20of%20excellence%20that%20has%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20government%20to%20help%20patients%20with%20rare%20disease%20treatment%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchangemakers-india-1738844473.jpg%20120