s%20Punjab%2C%20showing%20great%20results%20in%20both%20water%20conservation%20and%20crop%20production.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20yield%20was%20on%20par%20with%20traditional%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kahan%20Singh%2C%20who%20harvested%2028%20quintals%20of%20paddy%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%20water%2C%20scripting%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaswinder%20Singh%2C%20a%20farmer%20and%20resident%20of%20Lambra%20village%20in%20the%20Hoshiarpur%20district%2C%20adopted%20the%20SRB%20technique%20last%20season%20to%20grow%20paddy%20on%20two%20acres%20of%20land.%20%E2%80%9CI%20observed%20that%20using%20this%20technique%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20save%20Rs%208%2C000%20per%20acre%20on%20irrigation%20and%20labour%20costs.%20As%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20standing%20water%20in%20this%20method%2C%20I%20only%20had%20to%20water%20my%20field%20four%20times.%20Earlier%2C%20we%20had%20to%20irrigate%20the%20field%20at%20least%2020%20times.%20Despite%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F143975%2Fdrip-irrigation-increases-rice-yield-of-tamil-nadu-farmers%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless%20irrigation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20no%20difference%20in%20the%20yield%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20farmer%2C%20who%20harvested%2024%20quintals%20of%20rice%20from%20his%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-3-1738222596.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Last%20season%2C%20Kahan%20Singh's%20method%20was%20adopted%20at%2012%20trial%20sites%20across%20Punjab.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-3-1738222596.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2F