arding%20experience%2C%20it%20also%20came%20with%20its%20share%20of%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManaging%20the%20hotel%20exposed%20them%20to%20a%20glaring%20gap%20in%20the%20food%20and%20hospitality%20industry%3A%20inefficient%20procurement%20processes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20how%20much%20time%20and%20resources%20were%20wasted%20in%20sourcing%20raw%20materials%20and%20managing%20supplies.%20It%20was%20chaotic%2C%20and%20we%20thought%2C%20why%20not%20use%20technology%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%3F%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Bharath%2C%20Dhanvita%E2%80%99s%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FMervin-Feature-image-45-1738592795.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20founders%20of%20Aecoz.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FMervin-Feature-image-45-1738592795.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FMervin-Feature-image-45-1738592795-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FMervin-Feature-image-45-1738592795-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FMervin-Feature-image-45-1738592795-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FMervin-Feature-image-45-1738592795-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-402948%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDhanvita%2C%20Srinidhi%2C%20and%20Bharath%20decided%20to%20fill%20the%20gap%20of%20procurement%20in%20the%20food%20industry.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20realisation%20sowed%20the%20seeds%20of%20their%20second%20venture%20%E2%80%94%20an%20innovative%20platform%20aimed%2