%20but%20what%20worried%20me%20most%20was%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20survival%2C%20even%20after%20spending%20such%20a%20massive%20amount%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2032-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20support%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20physical%20toll%20of%20the%20treatment%20was%20exhausting%3B%20the%20young%20man%20endured%2012%20rounds%20of%20chemotherapy%2C%20each%20one%20taking%20an%20increasingly%20heavy%20toll%20on%20his%20body%2C%20and%20leaving%20him%20weaker%20and%20more%20vulnerable%20than%20the%20last.%20%E2%80%9CI%20lost%20my%20immunity%2C%20my%20hair%2C%20and%20all%20my%20energy.%20I%20would%20often%20feel%20nauseous%20and%20incredibly%20fatigued%20after%20each%20session%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20these%20difficult%20times%20that%20his%20brother%2C%20Srroth%20Bhartesh%2C%20emerged%20as%20his%20greatest%20pillar%20of%20support.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20days%20when%20Harteij%20hit%20rock%20bottom%2C%20and%20nothing%20seemed%20to%20help.%20But%20I%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20stay%20by%20his%20side%2C%20talk%20to%20him%2C%20and%20keep%20his%20mind%20occupied%20with%20positive%20thoughts%20to%20help%20him%20push%20through%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srroth%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20never%20spoke%20much%20about%20his%20condition%20to%20us.%20He%20wanted%20us%20to%20stay%20hopeful%2C%20even%20when%20things%20were%20tough.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20months%2C%20Harteij%E2%80%99s%20mother%20remained%20unaware%20of%20the%20severity%20of%20his%20illness.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20until%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342777%2Fprevent-hair-lo